'''Bactade''' was an edible form of [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] that was introduced some time prior to [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]]. A muddy liquid that was dispensed in bottles, bactade possessed good healing qualities, however it had a terrible, chalky taste. During their attempt to retrieve the [[Moss painting/Legends|moss painting]] ''[[Killik Twilight]]'' and the [[Shadowcast|code module]] ensconced within while on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], both [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] had to take bactade in order to heal their injuries.<ref name="TG">''[[Tatooine Ghost]]''</ref>

